title: My Top Nine
paragraphs: An online favorites list, My Top Nine, allows users to create accounts and form categorized lists of up to 9 items.
bullets: Performed as a Front-End Developer on a remote team of 5 consisting of 1 UI Developer, 3 Front-End Developers, and 1 Back-End Developer.
Constructed a themed and responsive single page application with customized Bootstrap 4.0 styling.
Programmed functional, state managed forms for creation and editing of categorized list entries.
Built using Axios, Bootstrap, JavaScript, and React.js.
